### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3002/api
@testUserId = 1

### ===========================================
### USER MANAGEMENT ENDPOINTS
### ===========================================

### Create New User
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "newuser_{{$randomInt}}",
  "password": "securepassword123",
  "displayName": "New User {{$randomInt}}",
  "avatarUrl": "https://example.com/avatar.jpg"
}

### Expected Response: 201 Created with user object

###

### Create User with Validation Errors
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "",
  "password": "123",
  "displayName": ""
}

### Expected Response: 400 Bad Request

###

### Get All Users
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Accept: application/json

### Expected Response: Array of user objects

###

### Get User by ID (Valid)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/{{testUserId}}
Accept: application/json

### Expected Response: User object

###

### Get User by ID (Invalid)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/99999
Accept: application/json

### Expected Response: 404 Not Found

###

### Get User by ID (Invalid Format)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/invalid
Accept: application/json

### Expected Response: 400 Bad Request

###

### Update User (Valid)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/{{testUserId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "displayName": "Updated User Name",
  "avatarUrl": "https://example.com/new-avatar.jpg"
}

### Expected Response: 200 OK with updated user object

###

### Update User (Invalid ID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/99999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "displayName": "Updated Name"
}

### Expected Response: 404 Not Found

###

### Update User (Validation Errors)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/{{testUserId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "",
  "password": "12"
}

### Expected Response: 400 Bad Request

###

### Delete User (Valid)
# Note: Be careful with this - it actually deletes the user
# DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/{{testUserId}}

### Expected Response: 204 No Content

###

### Delete User (Invalid ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/99999

### Expected Response: 404 Not Found